      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZEEZEEZOOM (1) comes here following a fourth behind Stripes at Group Three level two weeks ago over 1660m at Albion Park. Should enjoy a lovely run and looks the testing material. MAYWYN TROUBADOUR (2) won at this track two runs ago before having his colours lowered at his latest appearance over 2040m here, beaten 3.5 metres. Has the benefit of a good draw. Meets a comparable field and he is capable of a much better performance. O B LEGAL NZ (6) fell last start over 2138m at Albion Park. Generally runs very well at this circuit so can play a big role. GLENLEDI BOY NZ (8) is in the mix if he can recapture the form from two starts back that saw him finish third over 2040m at this course. One for the exotics players.",
